Updating Russian

title: Updating Russian
message:
Updating Russian

Just decided to update Russian translation, because the current one doesn`t look like translation, it just spoils all your work for Russian users. I, for the instance, have to switch to English to understand anything. 
I translate many apps, you can see some in my G+ profile (http://google.com/+DmitryGaich/about). Tried to make the translation in POEditor, but the main language there is somehow set as Vietnamese, not English, so I downloaded the original strings from github and imported my translation to POEditor. Anyway, as I see, the github file contains much more strings than the POEditor one, I see additional descriptions here - that`s why I translated everything and want to make this pull request.

title: First big push for new design.  Lots of work.  Starting a refactoring effort
message: First big push for new design.  Lots of work.  Starting a refactoring effort before moving forward, now that I have a better understanding of fragment lifecycles, action bar, navigation drawer, and all the other fancy new stuff in these API levels.  Kids these days have it SO easy.  Back in my day, we had to hand-code our animations, and we didn't have this fancy concept of fragments.  In the snow, uphill, both ways.  And we were glad for it\!
